snippet.title: Aquaman - Final Trailer (2018) Jason Momoa, Amber Heard
snippet.description:
This latest trailer gives us a look at the origin story of Aquaman, and more. The movie, directed by James Wan and starring Jason Momoa, will be released in theaters on December 21.

Aquaman Trailer (5 Minutes of Footage):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=N40xqhTuR5o
